        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " those who had taken Athaliah prisoner, \"let her loose\" till she got out of the temple court. It is also a common medical term for the cessation or remission of pain or disease. St. Paul uses it four times in his Epistles for \"rest\" or \"ease\" (",
        "children": []
